OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 10 Apr to Sun 19 Apr
OL,6,FChangeable with Atlantic frontal
OL,7,Fsystems moving across the UK at times.
OL,8,FThese will bring spells of unsettled
OL,9,Fweather, with showers or longer spells
OL,10,Fof rain and a risk of strong winds.
OL,11,FThe wettest conditions will probably
OL,12,Fbe in the northwest of the UK, with a
OL,13,Frisk of snow on high ground in the
OL,14,Fnorth. Drier and brighter interludes
OL,15,Fwith lighter winds will develop
OL,16,Fbetween frontal systems. Temperatures
OL,17,Fare expected to be close to average
OL,18,Foverall, perhaps with some colder
OL,19,Fspells in the north and warmer
OL,20,Fconditions in the south at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
